"uid":32217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T06:24:40.000Z","msg":"睇過好多專科都搵唔到原因<br />\n一兩個月就痛一次<br />\n頭痛+想嘔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T06:26:16.000Z","msg":"一兩個月先痛一次對我嚟講已經好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我日日都痛"},{"pid":"289a2e1880625f3fa8a45be91eec8841ecfd105c","tid":2159980,"uid":69020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a349eca90abfae4850da163d3c3f15a8397dcc2","tid":2159980,"uid":198375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T06:25:47.000Z","msg":"頭痛左30年 永遠都係同一個位痛 當然有時會痛既範圍大左半邊面都痛<br />\n<br />\n照過機又冇咩特別野 <br />\n醫生話可能條神經太近血管 有時壓到神經就痛 冇得搞 唯有食止痛藥<br />\n<br />\n普通撲熱息痛，即係必理痛既成份已經係冇用，頭痛要食布洛芬既止痛藥，即係日本Eve 何隻牌子何d 爽好多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T06:28:33.000Z","msg":"我反而係食布洛芬冇乜用，就算有用都要幾個鐘先發揮藥效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但食特效必理痛就快靚正"},{"pid":"f844b91a755a4f906a6757b661bc81d501aeabe9","tid":2159980,"uid":78383,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T06:58:57.000Z","msg":"痛左30年<br />\n自從開始運動＋飲番夠水之後幾個月冇痛過<br />\n白痛左30年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7666f6264c0e008567a8c476a67627d5dcc21aa","tid":2159980,"uid":100934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T13:41:32.000Z","msg":"有可能係耳水不平衡<br />\n亦可能係條頸歪左<br />\n真係要check下先知"},{"pid":"e3549219482225b12720f4dbccf3b6357264bd6e","tid":2159980,"uid":32217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ad61e8cfe931a4f527fe6cdeb561f1181468d9e","tid":2159980,"uid":69020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb3b3afc7ca3349040418b2211f1b27eb08f2761","tid":2159980,"uid":32217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T06:24:40.000Z","msg":"睇過好多專科都搵唔到原因<br />\n一兩個月就痛一次<br />\n頭痛+想嘔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T06:26:16.000Z","msg":"一兩個月先痛一次對我嚟講已經好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我日日都痛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T16:13:17.000Z","msg":"早兩日先痛完<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一痛就痛足一兩日"},{"pid":"ccdd17199259ae491976e57ad2756b1419545ef6","tid":2159980,"uid":158993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T16:28:25.000Z","msg":"一個月都有幾次頭痛！頭痛多數係天靈蓋個位痛，或者太陽穴痛。之前試過頭痛咗成個禮拜，直頭影響我正常生活，成個人冇晒心機。"},{"pid":"987f6dad57b3da4a5946a62e945ca84da5e35ce5","tid":2159980,"uid":71354,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T16:45:13.000Z","msg":"我成日頭痛<br />\n好似有轟炸機炸落個頭咁<br />\n痛到面骨眼骨全部都痛<br />\n<br />\n最慘係訓教前痛諗住訓醒好啲啦<br />\n一醒佢個仆街又痛過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家慘到訓多一兩個鍾頭都痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個月至少痛足七八日<br />\n個七八日想斬咗佢放低個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"411bfd018bfc464f9aed0761c5a4085121b6fa24","tid":2159980,"uid":266621,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T17:55:05.000Z","msg":"我十幾歲起就有偏頭痛問題<br />\n後尾枕赤赤下，或者太陽穴兩邊扯住痛<br />\n有時係眼窩入面痛，好似比人打左一拳後既疼痛感覺<br />\n<br />\n訓得太少或太多，無飲咖啡，睇到閃光，突然大既聲響都會引發<br />\n太嚴重就一定要嘔出嚟<br />\n唔太嚴重食必理痛就會好<br />\n<br />\n作息定時，飲水多果排會好啲"},{"pid":"c9442aae26c814d644416979adb8d9e6631aab79","tid":2159980,"uid":110992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T18:27:46.000Z","msg":"次次飲完奶茶都頭痛 想嘔 點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d7b884ce1d9cefa44d2217aa77e55b7eea2849","tid":2159980,"uid":217607,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c9867f9c60dc2e632459fb2bc3058391e9e12b55","tid":2159980,"uid":69020,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"75fab9d707c720da0f5b2e9e355a26f8f41da6db","tid":2159980,"uid":156393,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a7ce91c49074b04723068a6a82dd4d1af8099b4f","tid":2159980,"uid":30688,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T16:19:07.000Z","msg":"冇因為咁樣睇過醫生喎，因為本身唔覺得係有得醫既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T16:30:43.000Z","msg":"我照曬ct MRI果啲 好在乜都驗唔到 最後淨係開咗幾百粒止痛藥俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我每日一定至少食一次特效必理痛⋯⋯<br />\n有諗過原因 偏頭痛或者係膊頭至頸嘅肌肉酸痛引致頭痛"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T22:19:40.000Z","msg":"同你一樣，每晚臨瞓都要食特效panadol<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T13:08:29.000Z","msg":"十幾歲開始偏頭痛 排到公立睇神經內科 醫生教唔好食特效panadol 因為佢有加咖啡因<br />\n日日有intake咖啡因 一停就更易頭痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b6a82d61ed2cec268fd387c0983f29321cc8780","tid":2159980,"uid":217607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"289a2e1880625f3fa8a45be91eec8841ecfd105c","tid":2159980,"uid":69020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a349eca90abfae4850da163d3c3f15a8397dcc2","tid":2159980,"uid":198375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T06:25:47.000Z","msg":"頭痛左30年 永遠都係同一個位痛 當然有時會痛既範圍大左半邊面都痛<br />\n<br />\n照過機又冇咩特別野 <br />\n醫生話可能條神經太近血管 有時壓到神經就痛 冇得搞 唯有食止痛藥<br />\n<br />\n普通撲熱息痛，即係必理痛既成份已經係冇用，頭痛要食布洛芬既止痛藥，即係日本Eve 何隻牌子何d 爽好多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T06:28:33.000Z","msg":"我反而係食布洛芬冇乜用，就算有用都要幾個鐘先發揮藥效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但食特效必理痛就快靚正"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T13:10:09.000Z","msg":"承上 可能都係依賴咖啡因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"134bfe2f161c2ba770ddf4913c3b6114c4deb0f9","tid":2159980,"uid":260954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T14:10:40.000Z","msg":"我都係十幾歲開始偏頭痛<br />\n<br />\n個時中一/二bodycheck轉介去公立專科，醫生判斷係壓力引致偏頭痛，當時因為無出現畏光等症狀，所以一直唔使照CT，次次覆診都拎百幾粒panadol走<br />\n<br />\n依家都keep住一個月痛幾次，多數第二日要返工當晚就會頭痛，左側後腦痛到眉心/右側後腦隱隱痛/成個後腦痛<br />\n都試過，通常都係跟脈搏跳動咁痛，不過轉左食EVE啦"},{"pid":"c934d0bbdcf24539b3b050ef3df7fc89685b05fe","tid":2159980,"uid":25573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T14:20:04.000Z","msg":"唔好食咁多咖啡因既野<br />\n細個偏頭痛 大個無咁嚴重"},{"pid":"975f8dc0d52d2f8264c2aed1a64ca614e79845b7","tid":2159980,"uid":39796,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T14:20:10.000Z","msg":"頭痛最痛嗰事要嘔先舒服d"},{"pid":"d1064465a2198778badc79d36c196545df908692","tid":2159980,"uid":69020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15d7b884ce1d9cefa44d2217aa77e55b7eea2849","tid":2159980,"uid":217607,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c9867f9c60dc2e632459fb2bc3058391e9e12b55","tid":2159980,"uid":69020,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"75fab9d707c720da0f5b2e9e355a26f8f41da6db","tid":2159980,"uid":156393,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T16:30:43.000Z","msg":"我照曬ct MRI果啲 好在乜都驗唔到 最後淨係開咗幾百粒止痛藥俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我每日一定至少食一次特效必理痛⋯⋯<br />\n有諗過原因 偏頭痛或者係膊頭至頸嘅肌肉酸痛引致頭痛"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T22:19:40.000Z","msg":"同你一樣，每晚臨瞓都要食特效panadol<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T13:08:29.000Z","msg":"十幾歲開始偏頭痛 排到公立睇神經內科 醫生教唔好食特效panadol 因為佢有加咖啡因<br />\n日日有intake咖啡因 一停就更易頭痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T20:42:56.000Z","msg":"但係真係好快有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁食咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇介紹"},{"pid":"0537ccc92fd7fb9ac7af680e19e146b4ab58c5c9","tid":2159980,"uid":69020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"134bfe2f161c2ba770ddf4913c3b6114c4deb0f9","tid":2159980,"uid":260954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T14:10:40.000Z","msg":"我都係十幾歲開始偏頭痛<br />\n<br />\n個時中一/二bodycheck轉介去公立專科，醫生判斷係壓力引致偏頭痛，當時因為無出現畏光等症狀，所以一直唔使照CT，次次覆診都拎百幾粒panadol走<br />\n<br />\n依家都keep住一個月痛幾次，多數第二日要返工當晚就會頭痛，左側後腦痛到眉心/右側後腦隱隱痛/成個後腦痛<br />\n都試過，通常都係跟脈搏跳動咁痛，不過轉左食EVE啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T20:49:10.000Z","msg":"我係小一/二已經開始頭痛，大概一個月痛一次，一路冇好過<br />\n呢兩三年痛得密咗，幾日痛一次<br />\n呢一年嚟更加係每一晚都痛，已經離唔開panadol，一盒30粒嘅panadol一個月一定清哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be7ef38c781336a3f13b24348e0f8d6fc7bffdd8","tid":2159980,"uid":69020,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"975f8dc0d52d2f8264c2aed1a64ca614e79845b7","tid":2159980,"uid":39796,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T14:20:10.000Z","msg":"頭痛最痛嗰事要嘔先舒服d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T20:52:27.000Z","msg":"我都試過，痛到食藥完全冇用，痛到爆炸但又冇嘢可以紓緩嗰下真係好無助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要唔知痛到幾時，痛足六、七個鐘之後痛到嘔，嘔完就慢慢冇事"},{"pid":"1056f6cae8ac30ac85ca6947a6da110f46a38290","tid":2159980,"uid":203662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T20:56:07.000Z","msg":"由細到大<br />\n每次喊得犀利<br />\n之後就會好頭痛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"947b8b10c93e40049a03f869cb0d60ab0064869d","tid":2159980,"uid":323855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d1064465a2198778badc79d36c196545df908692","tid":2159980,"uid":69020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15d7b884ce1d9cefa44d2217aa77e55b7eea2849","tid":2159980,"uid":217607,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c9867f9c60dc2e632459fb2bc3058391e9e12b55","tid":2159980,"uid":69020,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T22:19:40.000Z","msg":"同你一樣，每晚臨瞓都要食特效panadol<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T13:08:29.000Z","msg":"十幾歲開始偏頭痛 排到公立睇神經內科 醫生教唔好食特效panadol 因為佢有加咖啡因<br />\n日日有intake咖啡因 一停就更易頭痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T20:42:56.000Z","msg":"但係真係好快有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁食咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇介紹"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T21:29:05.000Z","msg":"冇特效個啲<br />\n如果你去到醫院咪食到淨Panadol<br />\n當然最好睇醫生知咩事"},{"pid":"c6fdfaaaf9b8497584c6f7ce6f33917edc373d42","tid":2159980,"uid":177924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:15:13.000Z","msg":"岩岩痛完嘔完<br />\n已經想放棄人生了"},{"pid":"1605ae5bb1c464dc714168154a91d49a9858567a","tid":2159980,"uid":177924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6fdfaaaf9b8497584c6f7ce6f33917edc373d42","tid":2159980,"uid":177924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:15:13.000Z","msg":"岩岩痛完嘔完<br />\n已經想放棄人生了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:19:02.000Z","msg":"痛左10個鐘<br />\n痛到個人迷迷糊糊咁<br />\n坐係床到痛到訓著 然後痛醒 再訓著係咁重複<br />\n食左4粒止痛藥<br />\n終於唔痛<br />\n但個人攰到咩都唔想再做<br />\n<br />\n有無人同我一樣<br />\n做少少運動/勞碌少少就開始黎料？"},{"pid":"f79e5b2c751a8f802cf53e2caaba3c888d3e1a72","tid":2159980,"uid":40222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:41:58.000Z","msg":"痛左十幾年<br />\n太哂太焗會頭痛<br />\n入戲院睇戲又頭痛<br />\n吃某D食物可能多化學調味又頭痛<br />\n(例:食杯面飲埋湯，Pizza 都間中會)<br />\n唔夠訓壓力大，太集中用腦又頭痛<br />\n訓太多又頭痛<br />\n好多年前照左MRI 正常揾唔到原因<br />\n嚴重的話會痛到作嘔，要Sick Leave 即刻食2粒特效必理痛訓一覺先冇事"},{"pid":"50f959ce43d986f6ea916ae2527cea1c49d537f0","tid":2159980,"uid":180982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T04:46:37.000Z","msg":"有時夜晚瞓覺前頭髮未乾 <br />\n朝早起身都會頭痛"},{"pid":"eca688b85fb27f08e1d984876af0c55ae437b132","tid":2159980,"uid":297465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7ce91c49074b04723068a6a82dd4d1af8099b4f","tid":2159980,"uid":30688,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b8d10161efde60f5f9c846b0c51363b4e1c6c076","tid":2159980,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T16:07:31.000Z","msg":"醫生點講"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T16:19:07.000Z","msg":"冇因為咁樣睇過醫生喎，因為本身唔覺得係有得醫既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T07:12:16.000Z","msg":"我之前都以為係咁😂但依家好返好多"},{"pid":"8aae037e1a740fc615a34a4f3398ea31de6460ec","tid":2159980,"uid":103481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T10:16:37.000Z","msg":"頭痛真係好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bed5d3ebfcde192964e953ace525ec55103d609","tid":2159980,"uid":1436,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T10:19:01.000Z","msg":"成日痛到想自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c451dff355ce53bc185644d3d9592b0e85a28605","tid":2159980,"uid":157261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T14:02:16.000Z","msg":"比風吹有機會痛<br />\n唔飲咖啡90%痛<br />\n有時飲左都會痛<br />\n係痛到冋果唔食藥會嘔個隻痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d90684c62f695ec00bbb34e47a1a65ad00ad4cbf","tid":2159980,"uid":125553,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T14:23:42.000Z","msg":"做得多運動嗰排唔會成日痛<br />\n一無做開運動一做又痛<br />\n太曬又痛<br />\n比風吹親又痛<br />\n焗親又痛<br />\n坐得耐又痛<br />\n太專心又痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係痛到想嘔咁痛<br />\n唔食止痛藥根本痛到郁唔到<br />\n但我都覺得係同膊頭/頸痛有關<br />\n做返多啲運動，令到膊頭同頸無咁痛，個頭好似都會無咁易痛"},{"pid":"f04801da52fe14cbad9f50f169d410ba78802e60","tid":2159980,"uid":342884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a349eca90abfae4850da163d3c3f15a8397dcc2","tid":2159980,"uid":198375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T06:25:47.000Z","msg":"頭痛左30年 永遠都係同一個位痛 當然有時會痛既範圍大左半邊面都痛<br />\n<br />\n照過機又冇咩特別野 <br />\n醫生話可能條神經太近血管 有時壓到神經就痛 冇得搞 唯有食止痛藥<br />\n<br />\n普通撲熱息痛，即係必理痛既成份已經係冇用，頭痛要食布洛芬既止痛藥，即係日本Eve 何隻牌子何d 爽好多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T14:29:36.000Z","msg":"Same here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食必理痛冇乜用<br />\n食EVE有時半粒都夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3df3c8e419683ac7563c17ce2314711fafaad498","tid":2159980,"uid":138523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75fab9d707c720da0f5b2e9e355a26f8f41da6db","tid":2159980,"uid":156393,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a7ce91c49074b04723068a6a82dd4d1af8099b4f","tid":2159980,"uid":30688,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b8d10161efde60f5f9c846b0c51363b4e1c6c076","tid":2159980,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T16:07:31.000Z","msg":"醫生點講"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T16:19:07.000Z","msg":"冇因為咁樣睇過醫生喎，因為本身唔覺得係有得醫既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T16:30:43.000Z","msg":"我照曬ct MRI果啲 好在乜都驗唔到 最後淨係開咗幾百粒止痛藥俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我每日一定至少食一次特效必理痛⋯⋯<br />\n有諗過原因 偏頭痛或者係膊頭至頸嘅肌肉酸痛引致頭痛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T14:31:57.000Z","msg":"有機會膊頭，頸嘅肌肉太緊"},{"pid":"57d93b5ba359799256c7fda8a33563c6b6c6d087","tid":2159980,"uid":342884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T14:34:42.000Z","msg":"原來咁多人都會痛到嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次頭痛都想快啲嘔到<br />\n嘔就真係舒服好多<br />\n幾日一小痛 間中一大痛<br />\n上個月有次痛到直情想跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}